---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="FLUX HOUSE | 南流山のレンタルスペース"
  description="千葉県流山市・南流山エリアのレンタルスペース。家族の集まり、ワークショップ、撮影など様々な用途でご利用いただけます。"
  ogUrl="https://fluxhouse.pages.dev/"
>

  <!-- ===================== HEADER ===================== -->
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="header-inner container">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img src="/fluxhouse_logo_yoko_0828.png" alt="FLUX HOUSE" class="logo-img" />
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-desktop" aria-label="メインナビゲーション">
        <a href="#concept">スペース紹介</a>
        <a href="#pricing">料金</a>
        <a href="#access">アクセス</a>
        <a href="#contact">お問い合わせ</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="hamburger" aria-label="メニューを開く" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-menu">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobile-menu" aria-hidden="true">
      <nav aria-label="モバイルナビゲーション">
        <a href="#concept" class="mobile-nav-link">スペース紹介</a>
        <a href="#pricing" class="mobile-nav-link">料金</a>
        <a href="#access" class="mobile-nav-link">アクセス</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="mobile-nav-link">お問い合わせ</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="hero-label fade-in">Rental Space — Minami-Nagareyama, Chiba</p>
      <h1 class="hero-heading fade-in fade-in-delay-1">暮らすように、<br />集まる。</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
        つながりが育つ家。<br />千葉県流山市・南流山エリアのレンタルスペース
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary hero-cta fade-in fade-in-delay-3">空き状況を問い合わせる</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== CONCEPT ===================== -->
  <section class="section concept-section" id="concept">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Concept</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">「暮らし」の延長にある<span>集いの場</span></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-body fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <p>
          FLUX HOUSEは、ただ「借りる」場所ではありません。まるで友人の家に遊びに来たような、
          くつろいだ雰囲気の中で人が集まり、語らい、新しい何かが生まれる空間です。
        </p>
        <p>
          「FLUX（流れ）」という名の通り、ここは固定された場所ではなく、人と人が交わることで
          その都度かたちが変わる、流動的な場所。南流山という土地が持つ、都市と自然が混ざり合う
          豊かさを背景に、この家がみなさんの日常に溶け込む特別な一日をつくります。
        </p>
        <p>
          子育て世代が多く集まるこのエリアで、家族や仲間と「特別な普通の時間」を過ごしませんか。
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://note.com/jin_sariimama/m/mbada4e66a2a3"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="concept-link"
        >
          コンセプトについて詳しく読む →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== USAGE SCENES ===================== -->
  <section class="section usage-section" id="usage">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Usage</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">こんな<span>シーン</span>で</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="usage-grid">
        <div class="usage-card fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="usage-icon">🏠</div>
          <h3>家族の集まり</h3>
          <p>誕生日会やホームパーティーに。広々とした空間で家族みんながリラックスできます。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usage-card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <div class="usage-icon">👩‍👧‍👦</div>
          <h3>友人・ママ友会</h3>
          <p>子連れでも安心。お子さんが遊ぶ横で、ゆっくりおしゃべりできる場所です。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usage-card fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
          <div class="usage-icon">📸</div>
          <h3>ワークショップ・撮影</h3>
          <p>ハンドメイド教室、料理教室、写真撮影など。温かみのある空間が作品を引き立てます。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usage-card fade-in fade-in-delay-4">
          <div class="usage-icon">💻</div>
          <h3>チームのオフサイト</h3>
          <p>Wi-Fi完備。少人数チームのブレインストーミングや、リモートチームの集合場所に。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== SPACE INTRO ===================== -->
  <section class="section space-section" id="space">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Space</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">スペース<span>紹介</span></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="gallery-item gallery-item--large">
          <div class="photo-placeholder">
            <span>リビング・ダイニング</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="photo-placeholder photo-placeholder--kitchen">
            <span>キッチン</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="photo-placeholder photo-placeholder--exterior">
            <span>外観・エントランス</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="equipment fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
        <h3 class="equipment-title">設備・備品</h3>
        <ul class="equipment-list">
          <li>
            <span class="equip-icon">📶</span>
            <span>Wi-Fi（高速インターネット）</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="equip-icon">🍳</span>
            <span>キッチン（IHコンロ・調理器具）</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="equip-icon">❄️</span>
            <span>冷暖房完備</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="equip-icon">🚻</span>
            <span>トイレ</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="equip-icon">🚗</span>
            <span>駐車場（要確認）</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== PRICING ===================== -->
  <section class="section pricing-section" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Pricing</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading"><span>料金</span>について</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-grid fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <p class="pricing-day">平日</p>
          <p class="pricing-amount">¥3,000<span class="pricing-unit"> / 時</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--featured">
          <p class="pricing-day">土日祝</p>
          <p class="pricing-amount">¥4,000<span class="pricing-unit"> / 時</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-notes fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
        <p>📌 最低利用時間：2時間〜</p>
        <p class="pricing-disclaimer">※料金は予告なく変更される場合があります</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-cta fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">予約・空き状況を確認する</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== ACCESS ===================== -->
  <section class="section access-section" id="access">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Access</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">アクセス</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="access-layout fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="access-info">
          <div class="access-item">
            <span class="access-icon">📍</span>
            <div>
              <p class="access-label-text">所在地</p>
              <p>千葉県流山市南流山</p>
              <p class="access-note">（詳細住所はお問い合わせください）</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="access-item">
            <span class="access-icon">🚃</span>
            <div>
              <p class="access-label-text">最寄り駅</p>
              <p>南流山駅から徒歩圏内</p>
              <p class="access-note">JR武蔵野線・つくばエクスプレス線</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="access-item">
            <span class="access-icon">🚗</span>
            <div>
              <p class="access-label-text">お車でのアクセス</p>
              <p>駐車場についてはお問い合わせください</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="map-wrapper">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3235.3!2d139.9!3d35.85!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x6018836d92ebf82b%3A0x96dab22f96b97e5b!2z5Y2X5rW35bGx5Y-j!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1"
            width="100%"
            height="360"
            style="border:0; border-radius: 12px;"
            allowfullscreen=""
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="南流山駅周辺マップ"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== AREA GUIDE ===================== -->
  <section class="section area-section" id="area">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Area Guide</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">周辺<span>スポット</span></h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="area-intro">FLUX HOUSEの近くにある、おすすめのスポットをご紹介します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="area-grid fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="area-card">
          <div class="area-icon">☕</div>
          <div class="area-content">
            <span class="area-badge">カフェ</span>
            <h3>レタンプリュス</h3>
            <p>地元で人気のおしゃれなカフェ。こだわりのコーヒーとスイーツでひと休み。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="area-card">
          <div class="area-icon">🪑</div>
          <div class="area-content">
            <span class="area-badge">ショップ</span>
            <h3>LIANTIQE</h3>
            <p>センスあふれるアンティーク家具のショップ。空間づくりのインスピレーションに。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="area-card">
          <div class="area-icon">♨️</div>
          <div class="area-content">
            <span class="area-badge">スパ・温浴</span>
            <h3>スパメッツァおおたか</h3>
            <p>大型スパ施設でリフレッシュ。サウナ、岩盤浴など充実した施設が揃います。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== MINPAKU PREVIEW ===================== -->
  <section class="section minpaku-section" id="minpaku">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="minpaku-card fade-in">
        <span class="coming-soon-badge">Coming Soon</span>
        <h2 class="minpaku-heading">民泊・住宅宿泊事業<br />準備中</h2>
        <p class="minpaku-text">
          FLUX HOUSEでは現在、住宅宿泊事業（民泊）の開始に向けて準備を進めています。
          「泊まる」ことでより深くこの場所と南流山を体験できるよう、準備が整い次第
          Instagramにてお知らせします。
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/fluxhouse_nagareyama/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-outline minpaku-btn"
        >
          <span class="instagram-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"></circle>
            </svg>
          </span>
          Instagramをフォローする
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== CONTACT ===================== -->
  <section class="section contact-section" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-inner fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Contact</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">お問い合わせ</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="contact-text">
          ご予約・空き状況の確認・その他のご質問は、下記のフォームからお気軽にどうぞ。
          通常2〜3営業日以内にご返信いたします。
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://forms.gle/MAnhrqk2x8Rn2JWD7"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-primary contact-btn"
        >
          お問い合わせ・空き状況を確認する
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== FOOTER ===================== -->
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner container">
      <div class="footer-logo">
        <img src="/fluxhouse_logo_tate_white.png" alt="FLUX HOUSE" class="footer-logo-img" />
      </div>
      <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="フッターリンク">
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/fluxhouse_nagareyama/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >Instagram</a>
        <a
          href="https://note.com/jin_sariimama/m/mbada4e66a2a3"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >note</a>
        <a href="#contact">お問い合わせ</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer-copy">©2026 FLUX HOUSE</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ============================================================
     HEADER
     ============================================================ */
  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .header-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 64px;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .logo-img {
    height: 36px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .logo:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .nav-desktop {
    display: none;
    gap: 36px;
  }

  .nav-desktop a {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    position: relative;
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .nav-desktop a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    transition: width var(--transition);
  }

  .nav-desktop a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .nav-desktop a:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nav-desktop {
      display: flex;
    }
    .hamburger {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  /* Hamburger */
  .hamburger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 5px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    padding: 8px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .hamburger span {
    display: block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-text);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) {
    transform: translateY(6.5px) rotate(45deg);
  }
  .hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) {
    transform: translateY(-6.5px) rotate(-45deg);
  }

  /* Mobile menu */
  .mobile-menu {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
    background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.98);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .mobile-menu.open {
    max-height: 320px;
  }

  .mobile-menu nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 16px 24px 24px;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .mobile-nav-link {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .mobile-nav-link:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .mobile-nav-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* ============================================================
     HERO
     ============================================================ */
  .hero {
    min-height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B6F47 0%, #2C2017 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 20% 80%, rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.35) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 80% 20%, rgba(184, 150, 106, 0.2) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2.5vw, 1.125rem);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 18px 44px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-light);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  /* ============================================================
     GENERIC SECTION
     ============================================================ */
  .section {
    padding: var(--section-padding-mobile);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section {
      padding: var(--section-padding-desktop);
    }
  }

  /* ============================================================
     CONCEPT
     ============================================================ */
  .concept-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .concept-body p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .concept-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }

  .concept-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* ============================================================
     USAGE SCENES
     ============================================================ */
  .usage-section {
    background: var(--color-light);
  }

  .usage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .usage-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  .usage-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 28px 20px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }

  .usage-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .usage-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .usage-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .usage-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #5A4535;
  }

  /* ============================================================
